posting_body: ['Spacious two story, four bedroom, two  bath home on a cul-de-sac street.', 'with formal dining, fireplace, amazing kitchen with 42 inch cabinets.', 'Incredible master bath with separate tub and shower.', 'Quick access to Northwest Freeway, just minutes away from shopping, Beltway 8 and Grand Parkway!', 'Christopher Fagan, Realtor, Broker', 'TEXT/CALL', 'show contact info', 'FREE SERVICE!!!!', 'Rentals Are Leasing Fast, Call For More Options', 'If home Is Leased', 'Are you Looking for a Luxury Rental Home?', "If you are moving from out of town, don't know the area, or simply just do not have time to search.", 'You can call a Professional Real Estate Broker and get help today absolutely FREE.', 'We Can Work With:', '☑ Relocating From A Far', '☑ Credit History', '☑ Background', '☑ Rental History', '☑ Need A Quick Move', 'We DO NOT Work With:', '❎ Income Below 3x Rent', '❎ Housing Vouchers', '❎ Section 8', '❎ Falsified Documents', 'Full Name?', '✏️', 'Direct Email?', '📧', 'Number?', '📱', 'Move Date?', '🚚', 'Price Range?', '💲💲💲', 'Locations?', '📌', 'Size?', '🏘️', 'Pets?', '🐾', 'Credit Score?', '📈', 'Privately Owned Home Rentals & Luxury Apartments.', 'We have experienced Real Estate Brokers and Property Management', "Don't waste time and money on inexperienced agents and apartment locators who do not have the experience or knowledge.", 'We match you and work to get you approved.', 'FAST!', '*Pictures are samples*', 'Please call me for more information at:', 'show contact info']
